{"tid":1642531,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"馬刺名教練帕波維奇力挺NBA總裁 遭中國網民咒：早日與亡妻相聚","createTime":"2019-10-09T17:58:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T01:59:31.000Z","uid":28765,"like":23,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"73c3fba7472a06e0a13f590f5682196a857da60f","tid":1642531,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T17:58:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_php1dQ1Xl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_php1dQ1Xl.jpg&h=f84a03a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n馬刺名教練帕波維奇（Gregg Popovich）受訪時力挺NBA總裁席爾瓦（Adam Silver）的「言論自由」說。沒想到竟有大量中國網民留言，詛咒帕波維奇早日與他的亡妻聚。（路透）<br />\n<br />\n2019-10-09 17:39<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕火箭隊總管莫雷（Daryl Morey）發推特挺香港反送中，導致中國官、民對NBA強烈不滿。對此，馬刺名教練帕波維奇（Gregg Popovich）受訪時力挺NBA總裁席爾瓦（Adam Silver）的「言論自由」說。沒想到竟有大量中國在網路上留言「祝帕波維奇早日與他的妻子相聚」，而帕波維奇的愛妻已於去年4月過世。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpznHwBT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpznHwBT.jpg&h=61e0c840&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n虎撲網民的缺德留言。（擷取自虎撲）<br />\n<br />\n火箭總管莫雷日前在推特上發文挺港，席爾瓦多次表態支持莫雷擁有言論自由，引發中國官媒、藝人和民眾強烈反撲，宣布停止轉播賽事、嗆聲抵制，但席爾瓦無懼壓力，堅拒對此致歉。對此，帕波維奇受訪時力挺席爾瓦，表示席爾瓦當年處理前快艇老闆的種族歧視言論時處理得當，也現身過同志遊行，力挺LGBT族群，「席爾瓦是一名非常開明的領導者」。<br />\n<br />\n沒想到，帕波維奇受訪言論被轉載至中國體育官媒《虎撲》後，竟有大量中國網民在底下留言「祝他早日與妻子相聚」、「祝他和兒子與妻子一家三口團聚」、「我直接祝他全家與妻子相聚」、「一家人就該整整齊齊」；有其他網友看不下去，表示禍及家人的言論太過分；也遭反嗆「已經相當收斂了」、「裝聖母？」、「攻擊的好」、「一點都不過分」。<br />\n<br />\n帕波維奇結褵40載的愛妻艾倫（Erin Popovich），去年4月19日因病過世，享壽67歲。帕波維奇和艾倫育有2子，他們還擁有兩名孫子。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2941577\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2941577&d=FZDcFY5BXo0CBgddFpFX57Xqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=7322fe66\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2941577&h=f739f383\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2941577</a>"},{"pid":"69120dfa1ee487b50295fd203a915475c87360a4","tid":1642531,"uid":94360,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T18:01:59.000Z","msg":"搞我波波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我屌你老母你班支那狗講啲野盡顯你地嘅質素"},{"pid":"2519ad0c5cb4fd663d52bfc64233bb39c6a0b9df","tid":1642531,"uid":62025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T18:02:42.000Z","msg":"Coach Pop<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ca1369c27059f2895f845cdbde83bd3aa9cdeba","tid":1642531,"uid":276495,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T18:07:06.000Z","msg":"支那狗真心唔識死 popovich絕對係依家成個nba最德高望重嘅人 咁都夠膽講出口 絕對會喺美國再升温"},{"pid":"dabd8d766db7db2183cd5c18b87e4e649a6d33c8","tid":1642531,"uid":49898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T18:08:26.000Z","msg":"推到俾NBA睇到"},{"pid":"3c0e25dbaaed94a70cab83f617767af8b171a648","tid":1642531,"uid":150742,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T18:08:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.gofundme.com/f/free-hong-kong-tshirts-on-nba-opening-night?fbclid=IwAR1qRUFOYUqnZXYZt9YxPl2WCIio1Q_oz29gN7IfJHeSnvr1wEHcqE05cls\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gofundme.com%2Ff%2Ffree-hong-kong-tshirts-on-nba-opening-night%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1qRUFOYUqnZXYZt9YxPl2WCIio1Q_oz29gN7IfJHeSnvr1wEHcqE05cls&d=FZDcFY5BXo0CBgddFpFX57Xqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=a149f06a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gofundme.com/f/free-hong-kong-tshirts-on-nba-opening-night?fbclid=IwAR1qRUFOYUqnZXYZt9YxPl2WCIio1Q_oz29gN7IfJHeSnvr1wEHcqE05cls</a><br />\n美國人集資係NBA開幕之夜派&quot;Stand With Hong Kong&quot; T-Shirt俾在場觀眾 搞到到時班大陸人連cap圖都cap唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n連豬話你地連Retweet咁簡單都唔做 點光復香港呀<img src=